BEGIN:VTODO
UID:TODO-D74C67FA-70BD-4D94-90FF-34701C3AD4A5
DTSTAMP:20260416T154900Z
SUMMARY:Aniketh Mikkilineni [@axm]
DESCRIPTION:<2026-04-15 Wed 13:00-15:00>\n1. ☑ purchase negatively charged 
 lipid\, either PG or PS.\n2. ☑ purchase Mb\; explore options to isolate fr
 om fresh meat.\n3. ☐ HB and AM: how to control and measure PO2\, which we'
 ll need for\n   saturation curve and P50 value.\n   • we may need to purch
 ase mixing valve.\n4. AM: why HCys as compared to other natural antioxidan
 ts
CATEGORIES:@axm,BRG
SEQUENCE:1
PRIORITY:5
STATUS:NEEDS-ACTION
END:VTODO
